{"tid":1415584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺少部分和理非變咗和非","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:28.000Z","uid":207710,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1d0fc41e5246ef4c32fb517e544e95e9f412be","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"失去咗理性<br />\n當你發覺自己講啲嘢同林鄭七八成似<br />\n就應該諗返運動嘅初衷「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n前線可能有啲唔夠禮貌<br />\n有時戰略會錯<br />\n但而家唔係學林鄭講咩「回歸和平理性咁表達訴求嘅時候」<br />\n連口號都要自我閹割<br />\n要求北京出手平亂走去、擁護基本法<br />\n我哋唔係失去理性，走回頭路呀<br />\n我哋係同前線兄弟爬山嘅和理非，唔係綁手綁腳嘅和非<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n連胡志偉都敢講呢句<br />\n你走去叫啲素人自我閹割？<br />\n話咩呢句口號係林鄭計謀？<br />\n唔好失去理性！<br />\n民意有用，係前線嘅後盾，但唔係目的<br />\n有得爭取民意要爭取，為咗民意放棄五大訴求係本末倒置"},{"pid":"1e41bf6d13a3946f44cf3f38df07bf129cff843c","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06ffc27df4dfc8c7646edf92fe836ee76b169aa0","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15e729f1e4cac0f861083be5148b60e4ee60ad1","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a235ea943bd54ab68d339a141432f525a73ce57a","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b472df6747d435f1ccd91b7e747cd697a6b73779","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01f87765ba53ae864dc38a781e0cfb01d65f0a4e","tid":1415584,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6440aaf791708920751dc3e01cdea1af02fa3ff","tid":1415584,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:00:26.000Z","